@startuml
title Online Quiz System State Diagram

[*] --> Login

state Login <<choice>>

Login --> TeacherLogin : [Teacher user]
Login --> StudentLogin : [Student user]

state "Teacher Login" as TeacherLogin
TeacherLogin : entry / Action needed
TeacherLogin : do / enter login credentials
TeacherLogin : exit / Entered into system

state "Student Login" as StudentLogin
StudentLogin : entry / Action needed
StudentLogin : do / enter login credentials
StudentLogin : exit / Entered into system

state MergeLogin <<choice>>

TeacherLogin --> MergeLogin
StudentLogin --> MergeLogin

state TeacherDashboard
TeacherDashboard : entry / After login
TeacherDashboard : do / Navigate to dashboard
TeacherDashboard : exit / NIL

MergeLogin --> TeacherDashboard

state "Create a new quiz" as CreateQuiz
CreateQuiz : entry / Option in dashboard
CreateQuiz : do / create a new quiz
CreateQuiz : exit / Quiz created

state "Edit an existing quiz" as EditQuiz
EditQuiz : entry / Option in dashboard
EditQuiz : do / edit an existing quiz
EditQuiz : exit / Quiz edited

state "Save a quiz" as SaveQuiz
SaveQuiz : entry / Option in dashboard
SaveQuiz : do / save the quiz
SaveQuiz : exit / NIL

state "Post a quiz for students" as PostQuiz
PostQuiz : entry / Option in dashboard
PostQuiz : do / post the quiz for students
PostQuiz : exit / NIL

TeacherDashboard --> CreateQuiz
TeacherDashboard --> EditQuiz
TeacherDashboard --> SaveQuiz
TeacherDashboard --> PostQuiz

state "View quiz results" as ViewResults
ViewResults : entry / Option in dashboard
ViewResults : do / view quiz results
ViewResults : exit / NIL

TeacherDashboard --> ViewResults

state StudentNotification
StudentNotification : entry / Notification received
StudentNotification : do / notification details
StudentNotification : exit / NIL

StudentLogin --> StudentNotification

state "Select a quiz" as SelectQuiz
SelectQuiz : entry / After notification
SelectQuiz : do / select a quiz to attempt
SelectQuiz : exit / Quiz selected

state "Answer the quiz" as AnswerQuiz
AnswerQuiz : entry / Option in dashboard
AnswerQuiz : do / answer the quiz
AnswerQuiz : exit / NIL

SelectQuiz --> AnswerQuiz

state "Submit the quiz" as SubmitQuiz
SubmitQuiz : entry / After answering
SubmitQuiz : do / submit the quiz
SubmitQuiz : exit / NIL

AnswerQuiz --> SubmitQuiz

state "View result" as ViewResult
ViewResult : entry / After submitting
ViewResult : do / view the result
ViewResult : exit / NIL

SubmitQuiz --> ViewResult
@enduml
